	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the iNES header, there is a number equaling the amount of 8kb CHRROM banks in it.
<br />If that number is zero, there is no CHROM so there is CHRAM.
<br />Games that have both of them are very rare and particular cases tough (TQROM board, I think).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


